<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; color: #1e293b; }
    .card { border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; }
    .footer { font-size: 11px; color: #64748b; margin-top: 24px; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>🚀 Your Weekly Drips Engineering Summary</h3>
    <p>Hi {{recipientName}}, here are top structural algorithmic friction blocks trending this week:</p>
    <ul>
      {{#each trackingProblems}}
        <li><strong>{{this.title}}</strong> - Requested by {{this.authorName}}</li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>
    <p><a href="https://drips.io/explore">Explore Active Coding Tracks</a></p>
    <div class="footer">
      Managed notification services sent periodically to your account. <br/>
      <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe completely from our weekly roundups</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>